videos.headline: Charleston's Babacar Faye slams down and-1
videos.description: Ryan Larson finds Babacar Faye rolling to the basket with a slick bounce pass for an and-1 dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Charleston's Babacar Faye slams down and-1) 2023/1/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charleston's Ryan Larson finds Babacar Faye for the pick and roll finish
videos.description: Ryan Larson finds a rolling Babacar Faye and hits him in stride for an emphatic dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Charleston's Ryan Larson finds Babacar Faye for the pick and roll finish) 2023/1/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Delaware's Jyare Davis shows off his court vision
videos.description: Jyare Davis hits a no-look over-the-shoulder pass to find Cavan Reilly for an easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Delaware's Jyare Davis shows off his court vision) 2023/1/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charleston's Ben Burnham gets it done on both ends
videos.description: Ben Burnham turns an emphatic block into a powerful putback slam on the other end.
